	      2.2 \amp -1.9 \amp 0.048 \amp 3.7 \\
	      -1.2 \amp 2.9 \amp 0.72 \amp -0.72 \\
	      -0.51 \amp 2.8 \amp -1.4 \amp 4.2 \\
	      -0.60 \amp 2.3 \amp 2.0 \amp -1.7
	      \end{bmatrix}</m>, <m>A_4=A</m>
	    </p>
	  </li>
	</ol>
      </p>
    </solution>
    <answer>
      <p>
	<ol marker="a.">
