	    </p>
	  </li>
	  <li>
	    <p>
	      <m>A_1=\begin{bmatrix}
	      1.3 \amp -1.2 \amp -1.2 \amp 3.8 \\
	      -0.58 \amp 0.56 \amp 0.56 \amp -1.7 \\
	      0.92 \amp -0.90 \amp -0.89 \amp 2.7 \\
	      -0.84 \amp 0.83 \amp 0.82 \amp -2.5
